lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, March 1 (AP) -- Acting Secretary of State Sumner Welles conferred half an hour today with Hjalmar J. Procope, the Finnish Minister. Mr. Procope brought Mr. Welles the text of President Risto Ryti's inaugural speech.
abstract: Conf with Min Procope and Amb Halifax on Finland
